13 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 52 O.S. 2021, Section 570.10, is
14 amended to read as follows:
15 Section 570.10. A. All proceeds from the sale of production
16 shall be regarded as separate and distinct from all other funds of
17 any person receiving or holding the same until such time as such
18 proceeds are paid to the owners legally entitled thereto. Any
19 person holding revenue or proceeds from the sale of production shall
20 hold such revenue or proceeds for the benefit of the owners legally
21 entitled thereto. Nothing in this subsection shall create an
22 express trust.
